data.revised_prompt: Visualize a masculine and powerful AI assistant in sleek cybernetic armor. The color scheme prominently features deep blue and silver, and glowing conduits of energy outline the robotics. His face is obscured by a glowing visor. The assistant is situated in a complex holographic command center, surrounded by floating screens and digital interfaces. Detail is high, mimicking a cinematic scene lit dramatically. Compose this as a 4k resolution digital artwork.
